1
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:55,740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

2
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:59,780
=Episode 13=
=Beneath The Sugar=

3
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:02,560
Chen Miaomiao.

4
00:01:02,720 --> 00:01:04,160
What on earth are you talking about?

5
00:01:04,320 --> 00:01:05,760
It was Hu Yitong

6
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,200
who deceived Ding Daang first.

7
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:08,800
You're a victim too.

8
00:01:09,360 --> 00:01:11,160
Why would you come after Ding Daang?

9
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:12,840
A victim?

10
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:16,160
Anyone who finds happiness
isn't really a victim.

11
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:26,280
Yu Kun.

12
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:29,840
Was it fun for you two
to make such a scene?

13
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:34,280
Get out.

14
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:38,600
Sorry, everyone,

15
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:40,360
for making such a scene.

16
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:42,160
Continue with the ceremony.

17
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,680
Continue?

18
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,360
Hu Yitong,

19
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,400
unless I die today,

20
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,600
you'll never get engaged to her.

21
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:53,440
That's enough.

22
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,800
I'm sorry.

23
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:07,200
Come with me.

24
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,160
I'm not going.

25
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:09,920
I don't want them engaged.

26
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,640
Come with me.

27
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:14,280
Wait a sec.

28
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:39,390
Ding Daang, what the hell?

29
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,000
She hit me.

30
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,800
You repaid.

31
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,080
Now...

32
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,040
we're even.

33
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:11,760
Let me go.

34
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,520
Brother, what's wrong?

35
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,720
Who told you to show up here?

36
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:33,160
Who told you to show up here?

37
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,400
Where's your med?

38
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,440
Don't touch me.

39
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,480
Who told you to come back?

40
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,280
I told you,

41
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,880
I'll take care of it.

42
00:03:50,290 --> 00:03:51,160
I...

43
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,400
I'll handle this.

44
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:56,880
Give me the med.

45
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,320
Can you take your med first?

46
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,800
Hand me the medicine.

47
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:06,600
Brother.

48
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,660
Brother.

49
00:04:07,660 --> 00:04:09,000
Ding Daang, drop the innocent act.

50
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,160
Was it fun for you two
to make such a scene?

51
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,800
Chen Aming.

52
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,640
It's been so many years.

53
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,640
You're still not letting go.

54
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,080
You think you can get out?

55
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,520
It's you.

56
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,840
You're the one
who locked yourself in here.

57
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,640
Coward.

58
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:43,960
Chen Aming.

59
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:46,400
You should've been gone long ago.

60
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,760
Then why are you still alive?

61
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,440
Aming.

62
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,160
Aming.

63
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,760
Aming.

64
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:09,120
Listen.

65
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,520
She's been calling my name all along.

66
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,360
Shut it!

67
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:32,680
Are you crazy?

68
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,120
If we stop now,

69
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,120
Yu Kun won't make it.

70
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,320
That's better.

71
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,590
He's barely holding on with meds.

72
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:38,680
Ding Daang, Miaomiao.

73
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,040
He doesn't even recognize them.

74
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:40,990
Chen Aming's personality

75
00:05:40,990 --> 00:05:42,120
is the anchor of his life.

76
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,840
Without his past,
Yu Kun's just a shell.

77
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,760
Have you asked what he truly wants?

78
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:47,440
He only wants to forget the pain.

79
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,480
Look closely.

80
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:50,360
Even now, he's still struggling.

81
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,440
Why do you get to decide?

82
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:53,240
He's in so much pain,
I'd rather he was gone.

83
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,360
Lin Xibei.

84
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,320
Have you even asked him?

85
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,360
None of us are him.

86
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,040
Listen carefully.

87
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:11,320
We don't have the right

88
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,520
to decide for him.

89
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,040
Do you remember what just happened?

90
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:52,360
Relax.

91
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,000
I'm fine.

92
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,640
And after that?

93
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,280
Do you want to know?

94
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,360
You fainted at a critical moment

95
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,280
of stopping a wedding.

96
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,000
So lame.

97
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,280
What time is it?

98
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,520
The ceremony ended ages ago.

99
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:13,520
I know.

100
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:19,100
I'm just asking what time it is.

101
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,480
Ding Daang didn't get engaged.

102
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:29,400
The scene was absolutely devastating.

103
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,000
Ding Daang.

104
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,440
Ignore those troublemakers.

105
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:35,880
Let's keep going.

106
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:38,280
We can't let them laugh at us.

107
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,080
Let's end this nonsense now.

108
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:44,960
What did you just say?

109
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,430
Ding Daang.

110
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,520
Get your head straight.

111
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,560
This is just a misunderstanding.

112
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:52,080
It was Yu Kun and his sister.

113
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,400
They teamed up to cause trouble.

114
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,160
I'm sorry.

115
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,400
Ding Daang, have you lost it?

116
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,760
Are you aware of the consequences?

117
00:08:06,870 --> 00:08:11,440
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

118
00:08:15,910 --> 00:08:17,850
♪They say♪

119
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:20,340
♪Lovers should never hold hands♪

120
00:08:21,110 --> 00:08:26,640
♪While watching a sad movie♪

121
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:30,140
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

122
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:36,310
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

123
00:08:37,690 --> 00:08:43,450
♪I've already lost you♪

124
00:08:43,450 --> 00:08:48,430
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

125
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,840
(Chen Aming,)

126
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:51,840
(leave me alone.)

127
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,320
(Get lost.)

128
00:08:55,180 --> 00:08:59,960
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

129
00:09:01,070 --> 00:09:05,100
♪The past will always pass♪

130
00:09:05,430 --> 00:09:13,020
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

131
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,160
(Boss,)

132
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:16,760
(I really wish)

133
00:09:16,870 --> 00:09:17,720
(you don't have to)

134
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:19,760
(become like this.)

135
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,680
(Hope you won't regret it.)

136
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,280
(Whatever you want,)

137
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,960
(I'll always have your back.)

138
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:38,680
Where are you going?

139
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:42,960
Do you even know your condition?

140
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:03,880
Where's Ding Daang?

141
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:07,800
Since you still care about her,

142
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:10,280
why keep leaving her again and again?

143
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,560
How much more hurt
do you plan to cause her

144
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:13,540
before you're satisfied?

145
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,320
Boss,

146
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,080
don't forget this.

147
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:45,400
You're here already.

148
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:46,720
Let's have a chat?

149
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,640
Chatting with me

150
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:50,200
is pricey.

151
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:53,280
Well, I'm not exactly cheap either.

152
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:54,840
Let's call it even?

153
00:11:15,520 --> 00:11:16,360
Childish.

154
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,400
Stay away from me.

155
00:11:43,770 --> 00:11:46,620
♪Everything in my memories
feels so beautiful♪

156
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:47,480
Does it hurt?

157
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,560
Don't touch me.

158
00:11:50,700 --> 00:11:55,270
♪In every photo,
your smiles are always so bright♪

159
00:11:57,650 --> 00:12:02,050
♪And there's that little cat
by the window♪

160
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:08,290
♪Always stretching relaxed♪

161
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,440
You're not Aming.

162
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,320
Am I not?

163
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,480
Then who am I?

164
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,440
He would never treat me like this.

165
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,560
Haven't I been good to you?

166
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,680
If I go with you today,

167
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:43,920
will you marry me?

168
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:00,760
You're terrible.

169
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:07,880
Yet you still broke off
the engagement for me.

170
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:10,840
That's because I promised Aming.

171
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,240
I'd only marry him in this lifetime.

172
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:15,160
I kept the promise.

173
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,200
But all of this

174
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,540
has nothing to do with you.

175
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:24,920
Ding Daang.

176
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,280
Get out here.

177
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:29,000
You've shamed the whole Ding family.

178
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:44,880
(Whether you're Yu Kun or Chen Aming,)

179
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,480
(it seems)

180
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:49,120
(we can never fully cut ties between us.)

181
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:54,040
(Ding Daang,)

182
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:55,800
(in your heart,)

183
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,880
(is there only room for Chen Aming?)

184
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:03,240
Ding Daang, have you lost your mind?

185
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:05,360
Don't throw yourself away

186
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,720
over people who don't matter.

187
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,320
And now you've even dragged me into it.

188
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,120
Let's make a deal,

189
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:11,840
Yu Kun.

190
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:15,600
All I need is just a marriag

191
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:16,960
with no real strings.

192
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,300
I'm changing the game plan.

193
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:23,760
I want everyone

194
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:25,920
to get what they deserve.

195
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:29,600
In this scene,

196
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,920
no one gets to walk away early.

197
00:15:01,250 --> 00:15:08,250
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

198
00:15:12,650 --> 00:15:20,010
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

199
00:15:24,460 --> 00:15:26,400
♪They say♪

200
00:15:26,810 --> 00:15:35,190
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

201
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:38,690
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

202
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:44,860
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

203
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:52,000
♪I've already lost you♪

204
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:57,480
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

205
00:15:57,780 --> 00:16:03,730
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

206
00:16:03,730 --> 00:16:08,510
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

207
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:13,650
♪The past will always pass♪

208
00:16:13,980 --> 00:16:21,560
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

209
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:25,280
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

210
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:31,490
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

211
00:16:33,950 --> 00:16:37,480
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

212
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:43,740
♪But sadly, it's not you♪
